# Everything under backend/scripts/ is local admin / seed / one-off dev tooling
# that is not part of the running app, so the whole folder is ignored. Use the
# /* form (not the bare directory) so the file below can be re-included.
# KEPT tracked via negation because code depends on it:
#   - reseed_db_from_registry.py : used by tests/unit/test_cross_platform.py and
#                                  referenced in routes/library.py (schema recovery)
backend/scripts/*
!backend/scripts/reseed_db_from_registry.py